column2: SELECT specObjID, bestObjID, z,rownum FROM ( SELECT specObjID, bestObjID, z,ROW_NUMBER() OVER(ORDER BY z) as rownum FROM SpecObj WHERE class = &&& AND zWarning = # AND z BETWEEN # AND # AND (survey = &&& or survey = &&&) AND bestObjID <> &&&) as t where t.rownum % # = #  order by t.rownum
